{"name":"Rift of Light","permission":{"default":0,"gWQQM82Hz7dxMdhO":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Casting Time</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 1 bonus action</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Range</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Self</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cost</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 1 superclass ability charge</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Recharge</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: <span style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre;\">[[/roll 1d6cs&gt;=6 # Class Ability Recharge]]</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Duration</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Instantaneous</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You summon a vortex of Light that swirls in a flat circle with a 5-foot radius centered on you, on the ground beneath your feet. You can only cast this superclass ability while grounded. Choose one of the following rifts to create when you cast this ability. The rift dissipates at the start of your next turn.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Healing Rift</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. When you cast this Light ability you and all Risen creatures of your choice within the area of the rift can immediately regain shield points equal to 1d12 + your Light ability modifier. Until the start of your next turn, Risen creatures of your choice who end their turn within the circle, or who enter the circle for the first time on a turn, may also regain shield points equal to 1d12 + your Light ability modifier. A creature can only benefit from any Healing Rift once on their turn. Your Healing Rift allows Risen creatures to regain an additional 1d12 shield points for each Light level you are above 1st.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Empowering Rift</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. Creatures of your choice who are standing within the area of the circle become Empowered (Stage 1). Beginning at 11th Risen level, your Empowering Rift grants Empowered (Stage 2), and beginning at 17th Risen level, it grants Empowered (Stage 3). Creatures lose the Empowered condition from this Light ability at the start of your next turn.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"5yHlK0qMZPCb9jUE"}
{"name":"Super Ability: Dawnblade","permission":{"default":0,"gWQQM82Hz7dxMdhO":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Casting Time</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 1 bonus action</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Range</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Self</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cost</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 1 super ability charge</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Recharge</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: [[/roll 1d20cs&gt;=18 # Super Ability Recharge]]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Duration</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Concentration, up to 1 minute</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You unfurl solar wings and summon a flaming greatsword made of pure solar Light into your hands. For the duration, you: emit bright light in a 30-foot radius and dim light 10 feet beyond that; gain a flying speed equal to your base walking speed, and you can hover in place; cannot hold any other weapons or objects in your hands (any weapons or objects you are holding when you cast this super ability are immediately dropped).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Blade Salvo</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. As an action, you swing your sword and hurl a wave of solar Light from its edge toward a location you can see within 90 feet. All creatures within 5 feet of the location must make a Dexterity saving throw against your Light save DC, with a bonus to your DC equal to your Light level. They take 3d8 + your Charisma modifier + your Light level in explosive solar damage on a failed save, or half as much on a success.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Armored Light</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. Your AC increases by 2 while concentrating on Dawnblade.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Phoenix Dive</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. As a bonus action on your turn, you can rapidly descend up to 30 feet at the cost of only 5 feet of movement. If this causes you to become grounded, you can make a shield recharge roll. If there is a target beneath you, you cannot become grounded, but you can make a melee Light attack roll (add a bonus to the roll equal to your Light level). The target takes the damage of your Blade Salvo on a hit.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">At Higher Levels</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. When you use Blade Salvo at a Light level of 2nd or higher, add 1d8 to the damage of Blade Salvo for each Light level you are above 1st.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">FOUNDRY VTT NOTE:</span></strong></em></span></p>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">modify saving throw DC based on light level and light DC</span></li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PGB pg:105","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":90,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"msak","attackBonus":"ceil(@details.level/4)","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8 + @abilities.cha.mod + ceil(@details.level/4) + ceil(@details.level/4)d8","solar"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"level":0,"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"6EC3MtO8zNiaeAEP"}
{"name":"Blink","permission":{"default":0,"gWQQM82Hz7dxMdhO":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Starting at 2nd level, your practice attuning your movements to your Light endows you with the ability to close into melee range not merely by moving through space, but instantaneously translocating across it. As a bonus action you can spend your melee ability charge to teleport up to 10 feet to an unoccupied space you can see, taking all carried and worn equipment with you when you do.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You have a single melee ability charge. If you spend your melee ability charge, you regain it when you make a successful recharge roll (</span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace; font-size: 1em; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal;\">[[/roll 1d6cs&gt;=5 # Melee Ability Recharge]]</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana; font-size: 9pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">) or complete a brief rest.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PGB pg:49-50","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"7sjZotpkrBDhRZbA"}
{"name":"Magnetic Grenade","permission":{"default":0,"gWQQM82Hz7dxMdhO":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Casting Time</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 1 action</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Range</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 20/60 feet</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cost</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 1 grenade ability charge</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Recharge</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace; white-space: pre;\">[[/roll 1d8cs&gt;=8 # Grenade Ability Recharge]]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Duration</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Instantaneous</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You focus your Light into a fist-sized grenade made of void energy, which you throw at a target you can see within range. Make a ranged Light attack roll, and add a bonus to your attack roll equal to your Light level. On a hit, the target takes 2d10 + your Light ability modifier in explosive void damage. If you miss, the target must make a Dexterity saving throw. They take half the damage of this grenade on a failed save.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">At Higher Levels</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. The damage of this Light ability increases by 1d10 for each Light level you are above 1st.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PGB pg:31","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"ceil(@details.level/4)","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d10  + (ceil(@details.level/4))d10 + @attributes.spelldc - @attributes.prof - 8","void"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"815so68S2XDOr3BQ"}
{"name":"Super Ability: Nova Warp","permission":{"default":0,"gWQQM82Hz7dxMdhO":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Casting Time</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 1 bonus action</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Range</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Self</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cost</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: 1 super ability charge</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Recharge</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace; white-space: pre;\">[[/roll 1d20cs&gt;=18 # Super Ability Recharge]]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Duration</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Concentration, up to 1 minute</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You draw an intense concentration of void Light into your body, charging every atom of your being with roiling, explosive power. While concentrating on this super ability, the following effects apply: your base walking speed increases by 10 feet; you hover 1 foot above hard surfaces and still water; you have a resistance to bludgeoning, kinetic, piercing, slashing, and void damage; you cannot hold any other weapons or objects in your hands (any weapons or objects you are holding when you cast this super ability are immediately dropped).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Void Eruption</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. As an action on your turn, you can unleash an eruption of void energy all around you. Every creature within 10 feet of you, other than yourself, must make a Dexterity saving throw against your Light save DC (add a bonus to your DC equal to your Light level). On a failed save, they take 3d8 + your Intelligence modifier + your Light level explosive void damage. On a success, they take half as much.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">At Higher Levels</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. When you cast this super ability at a Light level of 2nd or higher, the damage of Void Eruption increases by 1d8 for each Light level you are above 1st.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">FOUNDRY VTT NOTE:</span></strong></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">modify saving throw DC based on light level and light DC</span></li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PGB pg:93","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8 + @abilities.int.mod + ceil(@details.level/4) + ceil(@details.level/4)d8","void"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"level":0,"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","for