 vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Duration</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Up to 1 minute</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You hurl an arc-infused grenade onto a non-living, hard surface within range. This grenade sticks to the surface and creates an active area in a 15-foot cone perpendicular to that surface. All creatures in the area must make a Dexterity saving throw. They take 3d8 + your Light ability modifier in arc damage on a failed save, or half as much on a success.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For the duration, creatures who end their turn within the area, or who enter the area for the first time on a turn, must also make a Dexterity saving throw against this grenade&rsquo;s effects.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Device</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. This grenade can be destroyed if it takes any amount of damage. For this purpose, the grenade has an AC equal to 13 + your Light level, and fails all saving throws.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">At Higher Levels</span><span style=\"font-siz