ertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Duration</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Instantaneous</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You toss a grenade of void Light onto a hard surface within range. On impact it breaks apart into a shower of explosive sparks. All creatures within 5 feet of the grenade must make a Dexterity saving throw. Creatures who fail their saving throw take 3d8 explosive void damage, and creatures who succeed take half as much.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">At Higher Levels</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. When you cast this grenade at a Light level of 2nd or higher, its damage increases by 1d8 for each Light level you are above 1st.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PGB pg:31","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8 + (ceil(@details.level/4))d8","void"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"atwill","prepared":false},"sca